00:27:43.090 --> 00:27:43.540
You say, wait a minute.

00:27:43.540 --> 00:27:44.180
Wait a minute.

00:27:44.180 --> 00:27:47.820
You cannot grow crops, even in
your back garden, without

00:27:47.820 --> 00:27:50.980
using something to control
weeds and pests.

00:27:50.980 --> 00:27:53.700
Everyone who grows cabbage
or lettuce knows that.

00:27:53.700 --> 00:27:56.550
The slugs will have it if
