intake of specific nutrients

00:30:41.210 --> 00:30:43.430
or nutritionally relevant
substances."

00:30:43.430 --> 00:30:45.830
Basically speaking, a
carrot is a carrot.

00:30:45.830 --> 00:30:47.460
It has the DNA to make
it a carrot.

00:30:47.460 --> 00:30:50.390
It can't decide halfway through,
oh, I think I'll have

00:30:50.390 --> 00:30:51.725
a little bit more protein,
or I think I'll

00:30:51.725 --> 00:30:52.720
do something else.

00:30:52.720 --> 00:30:56.320
It's hard work to be a carrot,
and it can do nothing else.

00:30:56.320 --> 00:30:58.510
So it doesn't matter what
you put in the soil.

00:30:58.510 --> 00:31:01.640
You can stop it growing by not
putting enough in, but if you

00:31:01.640 --> 00:31:06.410
put organic in or inorganic in,
it will absorb the ions,

00:31:06.410 --> 00:31:09.570
and it will never know
the difference.

