locally grown rapeseed oil, we

00:36:48.770 --> 00:36:51.430
would need the entire County
Louth just to provide Dublin

00:36:51.430 --> 00:36:52.610
with that oil.

00:36:52.610 --> 00:36:54.160
I don't know what Cork,
Limerick, Waterford, and

00:36:54.160 --> 00:36:56.070
others, and Belfast would do.

00:36:56.070 --> 00:36:57.270
But basically we've got Louth.

00:36:57.270 --> 00:36:58.590
Thank you very much.

00:36:58.590 --> 00:37:01.010
What we do for the rest of
our foods, I don't know.

00:37:01.010 --> 00:37:03.860
But it's very easy for
individuals to

00:37:03.860 --> 00:37:04.970
go after local food.

00:37:04.970 --> 00:37:07.110
It would be impossible for a
city like the size of Dublin,

00:37:07.110 --> 00:37:11.550
or even Mexico-- take a really
big city-- or Beijing,

00:37:11.550 --> 00:37:14.840
impossible for them to think
about local food.

00:37:14.840 --> 00:37:16.760
You are going to require
a huge food chain.

00:37:16.760 --> 00:37:19.560
You are going to work
trade and export.

00:37:19.560 --> 00:37:22.160
And finally, this little fellow
was born yesterday,

00:37:22.160 --> 00:37:26.406
exactly 24 hours ago, so
