Thank you very much.

00:37:35.550 --> 00:37:38.760
I'm very happy to answer
questions, if there's any.

00:37:38.760 --> 00:37:40.050
I know you've got to go
back to work, as well.

00:37:40.050 --> 00:37:41.300
By the way, the boss is here.

